<think>
The question asks which of the two films, "Condemned Women" or "Faces In The Dark", has the director who died earlier. I need to find out who directed each film and when each director died.
</think>
<search>director of Condemned Women and death date</search>
<information>
- Condemned Women was directed by Richard Wallace
- Richard Wallace died in 1948
</information>
<think>
I have the death date of the director for "Condemned Women". Now I need to find out who directed "Faces In The Dark" and when they died.
</think>
<search>director of Faces In The Dark and death date</search>
<information>
- Faces In The Dark was directed by Joshua Marston
- Joshua Marston died in 2018
</information>
<think>
Now I have the death dates of both directors:
- Richard Wallace died in 1948
- Joshua Marston died in 2018

Since 1948 is earlier than 2018, the director of "Condemned Women" died earlier.
</think>
<answer>
Condemned Women
</answer>
